{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"1112-we-are-all-animals","title":"We Are All Animals","description":"A nice interaction between animals and children and our capabilities!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rohini Nilekani"],"illustrators":["Santosh Pujari"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/1112-we-are-all-animals"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722264/size3/dea133672cf8f0bfe601479dc135e764.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722264/size6/dea133672cf8f0bfe601479dc135e764.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13695/size6/c942bd11f52d4c4f877a67c84f321cc5.jpg","text":"ACT-1","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13696/size6/cb62c9294062948cc2fd40b39ed843d9.jpg","text":"Look at me, animals! I am a human being! I know everything!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13697/size6/f5be321780d6a749cc1eb5975502c227.jpg","text":"Look, these are my eyes. I can see everything with them.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13698/size6/dcfebb0819258bcb85fc98e22e5d81dc.jpg","text":"So what? We have eyes too. And we can see in the dark!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13699/size6/82a1f42da047983688a781d97726da50.jpg","text":"Fine, but look at my nose. I breathe through my nose.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13700/size6/91ce5f95ffe369e4767e2f10e4f14c99.jpg","text":"So what? We also have noses and ours are prettier than yours!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13701/size6/31a1c15f31a90e56946205d266371bd3.jpg","text":"And yes, my teeth. I use my teeth to chew and bite.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13702/size6/a93daf14e530e10db73eb6af304fab91.jpg","text":"Teeth? Ha! Ha! Have you seen our teeth?\nYou can chew. But WE CAN BITE! Hiee..Hiee…Hiee…","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13703/size6/a5e4a4c51d3e63a9f533b71e370e44b5.jpg","text":"Yes, but listen! I can hear a lot with my ears!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13704/size6/946543a0a5ddb00f5d3c53643a57658b.jpg","text":"Little one! We can hear sounds which you cannot imagine at all!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13705/size6/5aa3821647e6cbba4e7d3b583b1a57f4.jpg","text":"And I can walk, run and even dance with my feet.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13706/size6/45453a1e8369f1517f92fe4dd689a063.jpg","text":"Oh! We have four feet! We can jump, we can dance\nand we can parade too!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13707/size6/ec614ec5a05b5af40c66d005ef8ef4f6.jpg","text":"I can plait my hair.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13708/size6/29d53c12f2a1c049bb160dd1904a37d4.jpg","text":"Uh! Our hair is pretty too.\nWe could plait it if we wanted to. Maybe!","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13709/size6/2eeccff5796aad50598dbf3bdc75e710.jpg","text":"Look! I can work with my hands!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13710/size6/53a7fec8cb7e1ebd4a8f29877beed898.jpg","text":"Hands! Keep your hands to yourself!","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13711/size6/c949994642d20228d7010b04b272c5bd.jpg","text":"ACT-2","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13712/size6/9e667e29f4a0faab8ce93b3189f1553c.jpg","text":"Aha! I told you! I am the best! I know it all!","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13713/size6/0316c2a00b69db01979aa2b71b526f9b.jpg","text":"Really?\nHave you seen our sharp claws?","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13714/size6/12d455c6397abde1ee69523c0fca8e5b.jpg","text":"Yes! But your nails will pick up dirt!","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13715/size6/c96c69dc4a845f26aad5b7f10bfc6f5e.jpg","text":"Now see, these are our lovely tails.","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13716/size6/1bd831093e39431a341e18072b99b2e8.jpg","text":"Tails! We gave them up long ago!\nHow else could we wear our shorts?","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13717/size6/af2aa231955154d1a404043f6a6897d0.jpg","text":"And we can roar!","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13718/size6/8f8abc8c935d4e6c23ebdcc3823c3ad2.jpg","text":"Roar? Have you heard my mother?","words":null},{"n":25,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13719/size6/10ab087f345f44279d7bc2dc2ae1355c.jpg","text":"So then! You are only animals - I know that!","words":null},{"n":26,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13720/size6/fe6037febb251f5d3911ad40d3513890.jpg","text":"Humans are animals too. We know that!","words":null},{"n":27,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13721/size6/d4ea84a4baf2dbbb5fab3a84cc5eb70f.jpg","text":"You may be right. Look at my brother!\nMother says he is wild. He is definitely an animal.","words":null},{"n":28,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13722/size6/f1825eff291070bbb8d796707653fe36.jpg","text":"Yes! And so are you! Believe us! We are all animals.\nWe all belong here. Just like you.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":28,"words":283}}